(1, 'MAINLAND', 'mainland', '<p><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: 400; white-space-collapse: preserve; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Business Setup on the Mainland in Dubai: Complete Guide<br /></span></span></strong>In the world of commerce and business, Dubai has made a name for itself thanks to the plethora of opportunities it offers, which cater to both entrepreneurs and corporations. </span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: 400; white-space-collapse: preserve; text-align: justify;\">Opening a mainland business in Dubai is a very strategic decision for anyone who wants to have access not only to the UAE market but also the Gulf market. With BSET DUBAI\'s help, setting up a business is beneficial and also very easy. <br /></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; white-space-collapse: preserve; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">WhyGo For a Mainland Business in Dubai?<br /></span></span></span></strong><span style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Mainland license companies are business </span><span style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve;\">formations that are licensed by the Department of Economic Development (DED) of </span><span style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Dubai, granting them the privilege of operating across the UAE and </span><span style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve;\">internationally. One would want to opt for a mainland business structure </span><span style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve;\">because it offers a simple way to:<br /></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">1. Access to the Market<br /></span></strong><span style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Mainland businesses enjoy complete </span><span style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve;\">trading rights across Dubai and the rest of the UAE. These provide companies </span><span style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve;\">with opportunities not only to access but also tap into such a diverse customer </span><span style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve;\">base and market, thereby prospering.<br /></span><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">2. Full Ownership <br /></span></strong><span style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve;\">So of late, foreign ownership rights in </span><span style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve;\">several business activities allow 100% ownership, because of which a foreign </span><span style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve;\">investor will not be necessitated to find an Emirati local sponsor while </span><span style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve;\">running a mainland business in Dubai.<br /></span><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">3. Participate in Government Contracts<br /></span></strong><span style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve;\">One rather benefits from being on the </span><span style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve;\">mainland, as they are allowed to bid for the various government contracts, </span><span style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve;\">which are normally very value oriented and are only exclusively available for companies </span><span style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve;\">running their operations in the main areas as free zones.<br /></span><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">4. No geographic limitations<br /></span></strong><span style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve;\">A mainland business, unlike free zone </span><span style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve;\">business, is not constrained to a specific locality. This flexibility gives the </span><span style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve;\">businessperson a chance to choose the preferential region within Dubai. <br /></span><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">5. Diverse Business Activities<br /></span></strong><span style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Whether you are venturing to be a </span><span style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve;\">trader, professional, or manufacturer all available in DED\'s long list of </span><span style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve;\">business activities, there\'s bound to be the perfect fit for your vision. <br /></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">The Facilitation of All Processes for Starting a Mainland Business with BSET DUBAI<br /></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Setting up a business can really be very tough, especially if you are first-timer to the business. With BSET DUBAI, everything is simplified up to completion. Here is what we do:<br /><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; line-height: 107%;\">1. Advisory Consultation <br /></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Our team closely examines your business idea, goals, and requirements to determine the activities that would be most suitable for your business under the specific legal structure and find the ideal fit after cross-checking it against the provisions of the UAE law.<br /><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; line-height: 107%;\">2. Registration of Trade Name<br /></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Selection of the best trade name is critical. Our part in this is to manage the registration with the DED in such a way that it conforms to legal conventions about naming in the UAE and is ready for proper reflection of your business ID. <br /></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; line-height: 107%;\">3. Business Licensing<br /></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%;\">You have to get licenses of the authority, which is known to be quite tough. BSET DUBAI would help you to take from commercial license, professional license, or industrial license applications and as other approvals for this license.<br /></span></span></span><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18pt;\">4. Office Space Solutions<br /></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">It&rsquo;s a legal biding for Mainland businesses to have office space; BSET DUBAI locates and secures office spaces in the most prime locations and makes sure that it complies with Ejari regulations.<br /></span><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18pt;\">5. Documentations and Approvals<br /></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Opening the account as well as other services, which might also involve licenses required for their operations and services. It would cover from preparing a memorandum of association (MOA) to submission of the tenancy contracts and related necessary documents.<br /></span><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18pt;\">6. Visa and Immigration Services<br /></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">At the same time, we also facilitate investor and employee visas by making the processing of documents simpler and much quicker. <br /></span><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18pt;\">7. Continuous Support<br /></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Offering services beyond setup through pensions and renewals services, compliance, and PRO as well.<br /></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Adding the BSET DUBAI advantage<br /></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">By partnering with us, you can take advantage of the very extensive knowledge and experience of our company at BSET DUBAI. The following makes BSET DUBAI different:<br /></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt;\">Tailor-Fit Solutions:</span></strong> Our service can tailor cut to meet the unique requirements of your business.<br /><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt;\">Clear Pricing:</span></strong> What you are quoted is what you will pay&mdash;we have no hidden or surprising charges.<br /><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt;\">Quick Set-up:</span></strong> We take the shortest time to establish your company earliest.<br /><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt;\">Local Knowledge:</span></strong> Our professional insights into the UAE legal requirements make it pretty easy to steer through challenges.<br /><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt;\">Specific Support:</span></strong> Will always be with our team, who are going to serve you at every stage on your path. Peace of mind comes with them.<br /><strong style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Costs of Setting Up a Mainland Business in Dubai<br /></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Mainland setup expenses differ depending on the nature of business, office site, and licence type. Rates come in the following form:<br /></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16pt;\">Trade License Fees:</span></strong> The fees start from an unacceptable AED 12,000.<br /><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16pt;\">Office Rental Costs:</span></strong> Rent is assumed at AED 15,000 annually based on location.<br /><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16pt;\">Visa Processing Charges:</span></strong> Investors and staff members both need visas that come with associated costs.<br /><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16pt;\">Permits:</span> </strong>Additional permits must be granted for certain types of business activities in the healthcare and education sectors.<br />Here at BSET DUBAI, we break down those costs to help you develop a proper budget for planning purposes.<br /><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Guidelines on How to Establish a Mainland Company with BSET DUBAI<br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt;\">Consultation:</span></strong> Discuss your business idea with our experts.<br /><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16pt;\">Activity Selection:</span> </strong>Identify the Proper Business Activities and Structures.<br /><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16pt;\">Trade Name Reservation:</span> </strong>Express with DED your unique trade name reservation.<br /><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16pt;\">Initial Approval:</span> </strong>Begin to get initial approval for the business with a name.<br /><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16pt;\">Office Space Leasing:</span></strong> Secure an actual office and register it in Ejari.<br /><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt;\"><strong>Documentation:</strong> </span>Submit all necessary papers at the DED office.<br /><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16pt;\">License Issuance:</span> </strong>Obtain your trade license and begin business.<br /><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Why Dubai?<br /></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Dubai proves itself to be a competitive and accessible business hub; astonishing infrastructure; and good, business-oriented policies and laws. As a city majoring in tourism, technology, real estate, and finance, Dubai allows entrepreneurs to come up with innovative ideas in one of these areas.<br /></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Join with BSET DUBAI Right Away</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"> <br /></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">The moment BSET DUBAI becomes your corporate partner, you\'ve won half the battle in achieving success in the usual setup of Dubai. Not only does BSET DUBAI provide you with management and efficiency, but also a networking platform to make your business set up or be compliant. Feel free to contact us now and begin your journey of successful business in Dubai.<br /></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">FAQs:<br /></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18pt;\">1 What Is A Mainland Business In Dubai?<br /></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">A mainland company is a collective entity that is licensed by the Department of Economic Development in Dubai. This allows the activity to take place anywhere between the UAE and internationally, unrestricted by location.<br /></span><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18pt;\">2. Can I Have 100% Ownership of My Mainland Business in Dubai?<br /></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Yes, the most recent reforms allow 100% foreign ownership to be practically opened for all types of commercial operations because there is no local sponsor needed for most of them.<br /></span><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18pt;\">3. What Are The Costs Of Setting Up A Mainland Business?<br /></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Costs vary widely depending on the type of activities, licenses, and office space, but generally start at AED 15,000.<br /></span><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18pt;\">4. How Fast Can One Establish A Mainland Company?<br /></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal;\">Depending on the class and expertise of the people you deal with, and this would be done in as little as a week or a fortnight through BSET DUBAI. </span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18pt;\"><strong>5-Why Choose BSET DUBAI for Business Setup?<br /></strong></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Seamless documentation coupled with expert consultation; of late, companies have been opting to establish their business with BSET DUBAI as they know they will receive excellent support.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%;\"> </span></span></span></p>', 'MAINLAND', 'MAINLAND', '2024-01-07 19:43:58', '2025-02-12 14:05:03');
