ont-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Freezone authorities&rsquo; approval is enough.</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 0pt;\">\r\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word; border: solid #000000 1pt;\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Cost</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word; border: solid #000000 1pt;\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Cost more to set up and run</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word; border: solid #000000 1pt;\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Comparatively cheap to set up</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 0pt;\">\r\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word; border: solid #000000 1pt;\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Business types</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word; border: solid #000000 1pt;\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Can have many types of businesses</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word; border: solid #000000 1pt;\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Only freezone-approved businesses are allowed.</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">FAQs</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">1. What is a free zone in Dubai?</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;Ans. </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">In the UAE, free zones are well-specified areas that allocate 100% ownership, no taxes, and simplified rules of conducting business.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">2. What are the types of licenses that are available in free zones?</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Ans. </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The common trade, service, industrial, and professional licenses are granted if the business is of this particular type.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">3. What is the average capital required to build a facility in a free zone?</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Ans. </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Actually, the fee can fluctuate greatly owing to the free zone in which the facility is being constructed as well as the specific kind of business.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">4. Why choose BSET Dubai for business setup?</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Ans.</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"> With expert advisory, documentation attendance, and tailored packages for a comfortable initiation of business.</span></p>', 'FREEZONE', 'FREEZONE', '2024-01-07 19:44:10', '2025-02-12 14:08:36'),
(4, 'OFFSHORE', 'offshore', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 17pt; font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">Off Shore Company Formation in Dubai<br /></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 13pt;\">An offshore license is a legal permission granted to companies or individuals to operate their business from a country different from where they live or where their main operations are based. This often involves registering a business in a country with favorable laws, taxes, or regulations, allowing the business to enjoy benefits like lower tax rates, less strict regulations, or privacy protection. Offshore licenses are commonly used in industries such as finance, gaming, and technology, enabling businesses to reach a global market while complying with local laws Top of Form<br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>Offshore Activities: </strong>Offshore companies can engage in various activities, including trading, investment, consulting, banking facilities, and tax benefits.<br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\"><strong>Tax Advantages:</strong> offshore license offer low or zero tax rates, making them attractive for businessesho looking to minimize their tax liabilities.<br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\"><strong>Asset Protection: </strong>Offshore companies can help protect assets from legal claim from the owner&rsquo;s home country.<br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\"><strong>Privacy and Confidentiality:</strong> Offshore jurisdictions often have strict privacy laws that protect the identities of business owners and account holders.<br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\"><strong>Common Offshore Jurisdictions: </strong>Some well-known offshore locations include the jabel ali, Ras al khaimah international cooperate centre, andAjman.<br /><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">However it is important to note that offshore companies Dubai are prohibited from operating within a domestic UAE market.<br /><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">They are used for:<br /></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">International trading<br /><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">Asset or property holding<br /><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #1f1f1f;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">Real estate, and intellectual property, facilitating strategic investment and wealth management.13 Sept 2024</span></span></span></span></span></p>', 'OFFSHORE', 'OFFSHORE', '2024-11-06 22:59:56', '2024-11-20 18:55:17');

