(2, 'Digital Marketing', 'digital-marketing', 'Providing digital marketing for your business', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: Calibri, Arial;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">DIGITAL MARKETING Digital marketing is the use of online platforms to promote products, services, or brands to their targeted audience. It involves strategies such as content creation, social media marketing, email marketing, SEO, SMO, Marketing automation, influencer marketing and paid ads to engage customers across various digital spaces. The objective is to build brand awareness, drive traffic, generate leads, and ultimately increase sales, leveraging data and analytics to measure and improve results continuously.<br /><br /><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">Here is an overview of digital marketing components:<br /><br /></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">1. Social media marketing<br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">2. Email marketing<br /><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">3. Content marketing<br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">4. SEO<br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">5. SMO<br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">6. Marketing automation<br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">7. Paid ads<br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">8. Influencer marketing<br /><br /></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">SOCIAL MEDIA MARKETING<br /><br /></span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">Facebook: - More than 90 Million Active User, Facebook is very fast Platform to reach all Customer Worldwide.<br /></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\"><br />What we do on Facebook: -<br /></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">Facebook Is Very Good Platform for Brand Creation, Product Awareness, Mass Publication, Lead Generation, etc&hellip;<br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">We Create Profile of Company, Dedicated Page of a Company and create multiple content in 3 ways (text, image and videos) with professional content writer and designer having more than 10 years of experience.<br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">Our team start joining Facebook groups of relevant industries of your business. And start promoting in all groups and pages every day.<br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">Our team creates Facebook paid ads as per your requirement.<br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">We will increased Business Page Followers, Page Likes and Post Share In Relevant Group for Brand Creation.<br /><br /></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">LinkedIn: -<br /></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">First we create business page.<br /><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">Then we add followers with the help of our expert team, We create content, increase connection and followers.<br /><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">Then our social media team start posting content in LinkedIn page and profile every day.<br /><br /><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">Instagram: -<br /></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">First we create page/ personal profile. Then we with make content in image or video format.<br /><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">We add followers with the help of our expert team and post it every day.<br /><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\"><br /><strong>YouTube: -<br /></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">We create business channel. Description to make video professionally by celebrity, model, artist, influencer, or animated according to the customer requirement. We shoot the video<br /><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">By a professional team in different location. We will publish video in YouTube channel and promote channel link and video in all social media, platform to increase subscriber in channel. Like share comment in channel.<br /><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">Our expert team increases subscribers on channel in organic way&nbsp;<br /><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">We have a team who increase watch time and hour in video. We will do in SEO YouTube videos by description, attractive headlines, SEO content, tagline, competitive ranking as per customer requirement.<br /><br /></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">WhatsApp: -<br /></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">First we make account and then business page, and then we make content by our professional team and post it every day to our followers and new contacts.<br /><br /></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">Tiktok: -<br /></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">First we create page/ personal profile. Then we with make content in image or video format.<br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">We add followers with the help of our expert team and post it every day.<br /><br /></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">Email marketing: -&nbsp;<br /></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">We do have more than 9 Year Experience In-house Team who are doing Email Marketing.<br /><br /></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">What we do in Email Marketing:-<br /></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">First we need content in email marketing in 3 format (text / image / html code) then we need company website/ landing page / contact submission form.<br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">We will start filter / gather the leads according to the Customer requirements / target audience of relevant business.<br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">We will create SMTP server as per customer requirement of monthly sending limits like 100k, 200k, 500k, 1M, 2M etc&hellip;<br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">Then we start shooting email with complete transparency and sharing a proper reports every end of the week.<br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">We do provide solutions as well if you have in-house team.<br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\"><br /><strong>Content marketing: -<br /></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">We make content in image, video, and text format according to our customer requirement. - First we create page/ personal profile. Then we with make content in image or video format.<br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">We add followers with the help of our expert team and post it every day.</span><br /><br /></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>', 'flaticon-marketing', '+971 54 375 7459', 'service_1732360097.jpg', NULL, NULL, 'Digital Marketing', 'Digital Marketing', '2023-11-08 22:40:15', '2025-02-11 13:49:26'),
(5, 'Sponsor Visa, ID Card Services', 'sponsor-visa-id-card-services', 'Providing Sponsor Visa, ID Card Services for your business.', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">Document We Required For Sponsor Visa / Investor Visa (TRADE NAME, LICENSE, PASSPORT, MEDICAL, EMIRATES ID APPLICATION, VISA CHANGE STATUS)<br /><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">Step 1 :- We Have To Book An Appointment For Medical Test Of (Sponsour / Investor) Normal / Urgent Upon Your Request<br /><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">Step 2 :- Once Medical Test Done After 24 - 48 Hour We Wil Get FITNESS Certificate Report<br /><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\" data-sheets-root=\"1\">Step 3 :- We Will Take Finger Print Appointment From Goverment Registered Typing Center Of Federal Authority Of Identity And Citizenship</span><br /><br /><br /></span></span></span></p>', 'flaticon-graphic-design', '+971 54 375 7459', 'service_1732619506.jpg', NULL, NULL, 'Sponsor Visa, ID Card Services', 'Sponsor Visa, ID Card Services', '2023-11-09 02:25:11', '2025-02-11 13:49:58'),
(6, 'Company Formation', 'company-formation', 'Providing the Company Formation for your business.', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">A great step for one to take, starting a business in Dubai, but not a complicated one at all. </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Company formation</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> has been made easy and stress-free with BSET Dubai. From a small business owner to a start-up and even to a large corporation, our team will help you in each step towards boosting the growth of your business.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Why Start a Company in Dubai?</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Dubai is one of the best places in the world to start a business. It has a great location, tax benefits, and policies that support businesses. When you set up a company in Dubai, you get access to a growing market, top-quality facilities, and a large number of potential customers. No matter what industry your business is in, Dubai is a great place to grow and succeed.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Dubai offers many advantages, such as allowing 100% foreign ownership in certain business sectors, no personal income tax, and easy access to international markets. Business owners from all over the world are drawn to Dubai because of its strong economy and excellent infrastructure.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Company Formations Types in Dubai</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">BSET Dubai helps you choose the right form of company setup. The main </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">company formations </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">available in Dubai are:</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 14pt; margin-bottom: 4pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">1. Mainland Company Formation</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">A mainland company enables you to operate in the entire UAE, even allowing you to bid for government contracts. The UAE has now opened 100% foreign ownership in several sectors, thus becoming an ideal destination for foreign investors. A mainland business enterprise is free to conduct business in the UAE market with no form of restrictions whatsoever. That\'s why people look forward to such a business in order to get maximum flexibility.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 14pt; margin-bottom: 4pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">2. Free Zone Company Formation</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The free zones offer full ownership, tax benefits, and quick setup processes. Each free zone is specially designed for industries like technology, media, or trade, ensuring businesses get the best support and incentives. The businesses in the free zones are best suited for people who would want to work on an international scale because of the customs duty exemptions and ease in importing/exporting.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 14pt; margin-bottom: 4pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">3. Offshore Company Formation</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The off-shore company in Dubai is ideal for a business that would like to keep its affairs private, save taxes, and enjoy asset protection. This setup is great for international trade and financial management. An off-shore company does not require a physical office in Dubai and is ideal for businesses requiring a legal structure without operating locally.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 18pt; margin-bottom: 4pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Business Name Registration in Dubai &ndash; Protect Your Brand</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Business name registration</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> is one of the first steps when it comes to </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">company formation</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">. Your business name is your identity, and it has to be according to the rules in the UAE. BSET Dubai takes care of </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">business name registration </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">for you to ensure that the name is available and in compliance with the law so there will be no delays.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Your business name should reflect your brand and be unique. It is important to follow the UAE&rsquo;s naming guidelines to avoid any rejections or delays. The name should not include any offensive words or religious terms and must accurately represent your business activities.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 18pt; margin-bottom: 4pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">How to Register a Company Name in Dubai?</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">To </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">register a company name</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">, follow these simple steps:</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Pick a Unique Name</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: Your business name cannot be identical to any other registered company in Dubai.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Adhere to the rules: </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The UAE provides instructions for business names, which include prohibition of offending words and religious words.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Submit for Approval</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: The free zone authority or Department of Economic Development will check and approve the name of the business.</span></p>\r\n<