INSERT INTO `service_faqs` (`id`, `service_id`, `question`, `answer`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(1, 2, 'What is digital marketing, and how does it benefit my business?', 'Digital marketing includes strategies that promote your brand, products, or services online. It leverages tools like SEO, social media, email, and content marketing to reach your target audience. Digital marketing can increase your online presence, boost brand visibility, and drive more qualified leads to your business.', '2023-11-09 00:34:17', '2024-11-20 17:34:58'),
(2, 2, '2. What types of digital marketing services do you offer?', 'We offer a range of digital marketing services, including Search Engine Optimization (SEO), Social Media Marketing (SMM), Pay-Per-Click (PPC) advertising, Content Marketing, Email Marketing, and Website Design & Development. Each service is tailored to meet your unique business goals.', '2023-11-09 00:34:26', '2024-11-20 17:35:33'),
(10, 2, 'How long does it take to see results from digital marketing?', 'Results vary depending on the service. SEO generally takes 3-6 months to show significant improvement, whereas PPC can yield faster results within days or weeks. We work with you to set realistic expectations and provide regular updates on your campaigns progress.', '2023-11-09 02:12:42', '2024-11-20 17:35:57'),
(11, 2, 'What is SEO, and why is it important?', 'SEO, or Search Engine Optimization, is the process of improving your websites visibility in search engine results. Its important because higher search rankings lead to more website traffic, helping you attract more potential customers and build credibility in your industry.', '2023-11-09 02:12:55', '2024-11-20 17:36:31'),
(12, 2, 'How do you create a digital marketing strategy for my business?', 'We start by understanding your business goals, target audience, and industry landscape. Based on this, we develop a customized strategy that might include SEO, social media, content marketing, and other tactics best suited to meet your objectives and drive results.', '2023-11-09 02:13:18', '2024-11-20 17:36:56'),
(13, 2, 'How do I measure the effectiveness of my digital marketing campaigns?', 'We use metrics like website traffic, conversion rates, return on investment (ROI), and engagement levels to measure campaign success. Youll receive detailed reports regularly, so you can see whats working and adjust as needed.', '2023-11-09 02:13:32', '2024-11-20 17:37:21'),
(14, 2, 'Can digital marketing help small businesses with limited budgets?', 'Yes! Digital marketing can be highly effective for businesses of all sizes. For smaller budgets, we focus on high-ROI strategies like SEO and social media marketing to maximize your reach without overspending.', '2023-11-09 02:13:46', '2024-11-20 17:37:51'),
(23, 5, 'What types of visas do you assist with?', 'We offer assistance with various types of visas, including business visas, employment visas, investor visas, and dependent/family visas for the UAE. Our team can help you choose the right type based on your purpose and duration of stay.', '2023-11-09 02:28:39', '2024-11-20 17:30:43'),
(24, 5, 'How long does it take to process a visa?', 'The processing time varies depending on the visa type and specific requirements. Generally, business visas take 57 days, while employment and investor visas may take 23 weeks. Well keep you informed throughout the process to ensure transparency.', '2023-11-09 02:28:53', '2024-11-20 17:31:38'),
(25, 5, 'What documents are required for a visa application?', 'The required documents depend on the visa type but usually include a valid passport, passport-sized photos, application forms, and relevant financial or employment information. We provide a checklist to make sure you have everything in order before applying.', '2023-11-09 02:29:05', '2024-11-20 17:31:56'),
(26, 5, 'Can I sponsor my family for a visa?', 'Yes, you can sponsor your family members for residency visas in the UAE. Our team can guide you through the process, including eligibility criteria, necessary documents, and associated fees.', '2023-11-09 02:29:16', '2024-11-20 17:32:19'),
(27, 5, 'Is it possible to convert a tourist visa into a work visa?', 'Yes, its possible to convert a tourist visa to a work visa in the UAE, provided you have a job offer and your employer initiates the visa change. We can advise on the process and requirements for a smooth transition.', '2023-11-09 02:29:29', '2024-11-20 17:32:38'),
(28, 5, 'What happens if my visa application is rejected?', 'If your visa application is rejected, we will review the rejection reason and help you understand your options. In some cases, reapplication with additional documentation or adjustments is possible. Were here to support you throughout this process.', '2023-11-09 02:29:39', '2024-11-20 17:32:58'),
(29, 5, 'Do you offer urgent or express visa processing?', 'Yes, we offer urgent visa processing for certain visa types at an additional cost. This can expedite your application if you need to enter the UAE on short notice. Contact us to discuss your options for express services.', '2023-11-09 02:29:52', '2024-11-20 17:33:24'),
(30, 6, 'What is company formation?', 'Company formation means setting up a business legally in Dubai.', '2023-11-09 02:31:11', '2025-02-11 14:09:13'),
(31, 6, 'How long does it take to register a company name?', 'It takes a few hours to a few days, depending on approvals.', '2023-11-09 02:31:22', '2025-02-11 14:09:44'),
(32, 6, 'What are the benefits of company formations in Dubai?', 'You get tax benefits, full ownership (in many cases), and access to global markets.', '2023-11-09 02:34:48', '2025-02-11 14:10:19'),
(33, 6, 'Do I need a local sponsor to start a company?', 'Not always. Free zone and offshore companies dont need a local sponsor.', '2023-11-09 02:34:59', '2025-02-11 14:10:44'),
(34, 6, 'Can BSET Dubai help with business name registration?', 'Yes! We take care of business name registration and the full company formation process', '2023-11-09 02:35:12', '2025-02-11 14:11:02'),
(35, 7, 'What are business consulting services?', 'Business consulting services mean helping businesses plan better, solve problems, and grow.', '2023-11-09 02:47:26', '2025-02-11 13:53:15'),
(36, 7, 'Why choose BSET Dubai?', 'We make things easy with expert advice and a good understanding of Dubais business rules.', '2023-11-09 02:48:32', '2025-02-11 13:53:36'),
(37, 7, 'Can you help me start a business in Dubai?', 'Yes, we help with setting up, registering, and licensing your company.', '2023-11-09 02:50:13', '2025-02-11 13:53:55'),
(38, 7, 'Do you provide financial advice?', 'Yes, we can help with budgets, cash flow, and managing money wisely.', '2023-11-09 02:50:28', '2025-02-11 13:55:09'),
(39, 7, 'How are consulting fees determined?', 'Our fees depend on the scope and duration of the project. We offer a variety of packages, including hourly consultations, project-based pricing, and ongoing retainers. After an initial assessment, well provide a clear pricing structure tailored to your project.', '2023-11-09 02:50:40', '2024-11-20 17:20:36'),
(62, 5, 'Are there any age restrictions for visa applications?', 'Age restrictions can vary based on visa type. For example, work visas may have minimum age requirements, and some categories of family sponsorships may have specific guidelines. We can provide details based on the type of visa you are interested in.', '2024-11-20 17:33:41', '2024-11-20 17:33:41'),
(63, 5, 'What are the costs involved in applying for a visa?', 'Visa application fees vary depending on the visa type, duration, and any additional services you may need. Well provide a full breakdown of the costs before proceeding with your application.', '2024-11-20 17:33:57', '2024-11-20 17:33:57'),
(64, 5, 'How can I check the status of my visa application?', 'You can check your visa application status through the UAEs official immigration portal or by contacting our team. We provide timely updates to keep you informed every step of the way.', '2024-11-20 17:34:12', '2024-11-20 17:34:12'),
(65, 2, 'What is PPC advertising, and how does it work?', 'PPC (Pay-Per-Click) is an advertising model where you pay each time someone clicks on your ad. Its an efficient way to get immediate visibility on search engines and social media. We help you create targeted campaigns that reach users actively searching for products or services like yours.', '2024-11-20 17:38:16', '2024-11-20 17:38:16'),
(66, 2, 'How important is social media for my business?', 'Social media is a powerful tool for building brand awareness, engaging customers, and driving traffic to your website. We manage your social media profiles to enhance your online presence and engage with your audience on platforms where they spend the most time.', '2024-11-20 17:39:04', '2024-11-20 17:39:04'),
(67, 2, 'What sets your digital marketing services apart?', 'We tailor every strategy to fit each clients unique needs, combining data-driven approaches with creativity. Our team stays up-to-date on the latest trends and best practices to ensure your campaigns are both innovative and effective.', '2024-11-20 17:39:27', '2024-11-20 17:39:27'),
(68, 15, 'What is a business license in Dubai?', 'A business license is a legal permit that lets you run your business in Dubai. It shows that your business follows the rules and is approved to operate.', '2025-02-11 13:58:02', '2025-02-11 13:58:02'),
(69, 15, 'What types of business licenses are there in Dubai?', 'The main licenses are commercial (for trading), professional (for services), industrial (for factories), freezone licenses, real estate licenses, and small business licenses.', '2025-02-11 13:58:28', '2025-02-11 13:58:28'),
(70, 15, 'How can I get a business license in Dubai?', 'You need to choose your business activity, pick a location (mainland or free zone), reserve a name, submit documents, get approvals, and pay the fees. Companies like BSET Dubai can help make this easier.', '2025-02-11 13:58:46', '2025-02-11 13:58:46'),
(71, 15, 'What is good about a freezone license?', 'With a freezone license, you can own your business fully, dont pay income taxes, and enjoy an easy setup. Its great for businesses that trade globally.', '2025-02-11 13:59:08', '2025-02-11 13:59:08'),
(72, 15, 'How long does it take to get a business license?', 'It usually takes a few days to a couple of weeks, depending on your business type and documents.', '2025-02-11 13:59:32', '2025-02-11 13:59:32'),
(73, 13, 'How long does it take to start a business in Dubai?', 'It will take a few days to a few weeks depending on the business type and location.', '2025-02-11 14:26:18', '2025-02-11 14:26:18'),
(74, 13, 'Do I need a local sponsor?', 'For mainland companies, yes. But free zone companies allow 100% foreign ownership.', '2025-02-11 14:26:36', '2025-02-11 14:26:36'),
(75, 13, 'How much does it cost to start a business in Dubai?', 'Costs are determined according to the type of business and location. A consultant can provide a detailed estimate.', '2025-02-11 14:26:53', '2025-02-11 14:26:53'),
(76, 13, 'Can foreigners start a business in Dubai?', 'Yes, Dubai allows full foreign ownership in most business areas.', '2025-02-11 14:27:20', '2025-02-11 14:27:20'),
(77, 14, 'What is a business advisor?', 'A business advisor helps businesses by giving expert advice on things like planning, finances, and legal matters. They help you make smart decisions and grow your business.', '2025-02-12 12:09:47', '2025-02-12 12:09:47'),
(78, 14, 'Why do I need a business consultant in Dubai?', 'A business consultant in Dubai understands local rules and regulations. They can guide you through the process of setting up a business and ensure your operations are legally compliant.', '2025-02-12 12:10:09', '2025-02-12 12:10:09'),
(79, 14, 'How can business advisory services help my business grow?', 'Business advisory services can help you create strategies for growth, improve your operations, manage finances, and find the best ways to enter the market.', '2025-02-12 12:10:28', '2025-02-12 12:10:28'),
(80, 14, 'What services do business advisors offer?', 'Business advisors offer services like helping with business setup, financial planning, legal advice, market entry strategies, and more to ensure your business succeeds in Dubai.', '2025-02-12 12:11:34', '2025-02-12 12:11:34'),
(81, 14, 'How do I find the right business consultant for my needs?', 'Look for a consultant with experience in your industry and a proven track record of helping businesses like yours. They should offer customized advice based on your unique goals.', '2025-02-12 12:12:21', '2025-02-12 12:12:21'),
(82, 16, 'Who requires a professional license in Dubai?', 'Any professional service provider, including consultants, lawyers, accountants, IT experts, designers, and teachers, requires a professional license in Dubai.', '2025-02-12 12:20:42', '2025-02-12 12:20:42'),
(83, 16, 'How long does it take to obtain a professional license?', 'It takes a few days to a couple of weeks, depending on approvals. BSET Dubai can help make the process faster.', '2025-02-12 12:21:05', '2025-02-12 12:21:05'),
(84, 16, 'What is a difference between a professional license and a freelance license?', 'Professional license in Dubai is for businesses offering services while a freelance license in Dubai is for individuals who are working alone without the company setup.', '2025-02-12 12:21:26', '2025-02-12 12:21:26'),
(85, 16, 'Do I need a local sponsor for a professional license?', 'No, you can 100% own your business, but you may still need a local service agent for administrative tasks.', '2025-02-12 12:22:21', '2025-02-12 12:22:21'),
(86, 17, 'How long does it take to get a trade license in Dubai?', 'Generally, it will take between 3 to 7 days for the license and the required approvals.', '2025-02-12 12:33:50', '2025-02-12 12:33:50'),
(87, 17, 'What is the cost of a trade license in Dubai?', 'It depends on the type of business, location, and license type. Contact BSET Dubai for a detailed quote.', '2025-02-12 12:34:09', '2025-02-12 12:34:09'),
(88, 17, 'Can I start an online business with an eTrader license?', 'Yes, an Trader license permits the sale of products and services online in Dubai legally.', '2025-02-12 12:34:32', '2025-02-12 12:34:32'),
(89, 17, 'Do I need a physical office to obtain a trade license?', 'For a mainland business, a physical office is necessary, but free zones and Trader licenses have different options.', '2025-02-12 12:35:37', '2025-02-12 12:35:48'),
(90, 17, 'How does BSET Dubai assist me with obtaining a trade license?', 'BSET Dubai can take care of everything from consulting to paperwork. It makes obtaining a trade license easy and stress-free.', '2025-02-12 12:36:09', '2025-02-12 12:36:09'),
(91, 19, 'What is the cost to register an LLC in Dubai?', 'The cost of an LLC setup in Dubai depends on factors like business activity, location, and government fees. Contact BSET Dubai for a detailed price breakdown.', '2025-02-12 13:21:05', '2025-02-12 13:21:05'),
(92, 19, 'How long does it take to register an LLC in Dubai?', 'The LLC registration process usually takes 3 to 7 working days if all documents are in order. We help speed up the process to avoid delays.', '2025-02-12 13:21:25', '2025-02-12 13:21:25'),
(93, 19, 'Do I need a local sponsor to register a limited company in Dubai?', 'If you are setting up an LLC in the mainland, a local sponsor holding 51% shares is required. However, free zone LLCs allow 100% foreign ownership.', '2025-02-12 13:21:44', '2025-02-12 13:21:44'),
(94, 19, 'Can I apply for an LLC visa after registration?', 'Yes, after completing your LLC setup, you can apply for an LLC visa for yourself, your employees, and family members.', '2025-02-12 13:22:04', '2025-02-12 13:22:04'),
(95, 19, 'What documents are required to register an LLC?', 'Basic documents include passport copies, a business name approval certificate, an MOA, and a tenancy contract. Our team at BSET Dubai will guide you through the full list.', '2025-02-12 13:22:26', '2025-02-12 13:22:26'),
(96, 20, 'How to register a company in Dubai?', 'You need to select the type of business, name it, get an approval, present the documents, and get the license. BSET Dubai takes care of all the procedures.', '2025-02-12 13:27:53', '2025-02-12 13:27:53'),
(97, 20, 'What is LLC formation in Dubai?', 'LLC formation refers to the formation of a Limited Liability Company. It is one of the most popular business types that offers protection for personal assets and facilitates trading in Dubai.', '2025-02-12 13:28:12', '2025-02-12 13:28:12'),
(98, 20, 'How long does it take to get an LLC registration?', 'LLC registration usually takes 7 to 10 working days depending upon the approvals required. BSET Dubai makes this process very swift and hassle-free.', '2025-02-12 13:28:33', '2025-02-12 13:28:33'),
(99, 21, 'Can I own 100% of my business in a Dubai freezone?', 'Yes, 100% foreign ownershipis permissible in UAE free zones without a local partner.', '2025-02-12 13:44:48', '2025-02-12 13:44:48'),
(100, 21, 'How long does it take to set up a freezone business?', 'It often takes a few days to a few weeks to finish the setup with the correct paperwork.', '2025-02-12 13:45:09', '2025-02-12 13:45:09'),
(101, 21, 'What are the main benefits of a freezone business setup?', 'Tax savings, complete ownership, simplicity of setup, and the absence of import/export taxes are among the main advantages.', '2025-02-12 13:45:28', '2025-02-12 13:45:28'),
(102, 22, 'Can individuals from other countries establish an LLC in Dubai?', 'It is indeed true that non-citizens can have 100% ownership of an LLC in Dubai, as the UAE is very open to foreign investors in most of the businesses in the country.', '2025-02-12 13:50:19', '2025-02-12 13:50:19'),
(103, 22, 'What is the minimum number of shareholders required for an LLC in Dubai?', 'In order to register an LLC in Dubai, a minimum of two shareholders should be involved.', '2025-02-12 13:51:01', '2025-02-12 13:51:01'),
(104, 22, 'How does a company of an LLC get registered and licensed in Dubai?', 'Getting your LLC registered in Dubai involves the following steps: named your company, handed over your documents to the Department of Economic Development (DED), which included the Memorandum of Association (MoA), took the initial approvals, and then applied for a trade license.', '2025-02-12 13:51:27', '2025-02-12 13:51:27');

